Package: fiRstore
Type: Package
Title: Gargle-based Firestore R client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Daniel", "Russ", , "druss@mail.nih.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4040-4416"))
Description: An R client for Firestore. A NOSQL document database
    on Google Cloud Platform.  The authentication is based on the Gargle
    package and the interface is based on the googledrive, googlesheets, 
    and bigrquery packages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
